article.linkText: Mogbo scores 19, San Francisco turns away Pepperdine 80-74
article.story: MALIBU, Calif. -- — Jonathan Mogbo had 19 points in San Francisco's 80-74 victory against Pepperdine on Thursday night. Mogbo added eight rebounds for the Dons (19-6, 8-2 West Coast Conference). Marcus Williams had 14 points and Ndewedo Newbury scored 13. Jevon Porter had 21 points and nine rebounds for the Waves (9-16, 2-8), who have lost six in a row. Houston Mallette had 19 points. Michael Ajayi finished with 12 points, eight rebounds and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
